# Andy/Russell full game.
# Source: https://www.wunderland.com/WTS/Andy/Games/HomeworldsPBEM/Game1Report9.html
# Player 1 is Andy. Player 2 is Russell.
# System IDs begin by discovery order:
# 0 Paradise, 1 Peace, 2 Cobalt, 3 Loverly, 4 Garden, 5 Jolly,
# 6 Freedom, 7 Shade, 8 Springtime.
# After Cobalt and Garden are emptied on move 48, later system IDs shift.
#
# The source notation appears to reference MYSB for Andy moves 5 and 9;
# those commands are encoded against Paradise, where Andy has the ships.

